ner S</collab><collab>Preusse M</collab><collab>Beutling U</collab><collab>Stahnke S</collab><collab>Pawar V</collab><collab>Rohde M</collab><collab>Brönstrup M</collab><collab>Stradal T</collab><collab>Haeussler S</collab></person-group><year iso-8601-date="2020">2020</year><source>Host-induced spermidine production in motile Pseudomonas aeruginosa triggers phagocytic uptake</source><ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/query/acc.cgi?acc=GSE141757">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo/query/acc.cgi?acc=GSE141757</ext-link><comment>NCBI Gene Expression Omnibus, GSE141757</comment></element-citation></p></sec><supplementary-material><ext-link xlink:href="elife-55744-supp-v1.zip">Download zip</ext-link><p>Any figures and tables for this article are included in the PDF. The zip folder contains additional supplemental files.</p></supplementary-material></sec></back></article>